The [[Template:Table|Table]] template allows editors to render tabular formatting onto the wiki.

{{Table
| h/1=Header 1
| h/2=Header 2
| h/3=Header 3

| 1/1=Row 1 Column 1
| 1/2=Row 1 Column 2
| 1/3=Row 1 Column 3

| 2/1=Row 2 Column 1
| 2/2=Row 2 Column 2
| 2/3=Row 2 Column 3

| 3/1=Row 3 Column 1
| 3/2=Row 3 Column 2
| 3/3=Row 3 Column 3
}}